{"tid":273713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[元朗撚]有無人覺得yoho好撚廢？","createTime":"2017-06-06T19:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T11:16:39.000Z","uid":16590,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88fea11f6138a594888443030295feecd2facfe1","tid":273713,"uid":16590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T19:12:59.000Z","msg":"吹到自己將會係大西北最大商場咁，但事實上個場就根本唔好行！新元中同midtown個商場啲鋪頭廢到無淪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行一個方向15分鐘左右基本上走得，因為連兜都無路好兜，明明yoho個幾塊地唔細，但係啲格局同設計就係差到仆街。遲啲3期開埋，除咗個戲院會有啲期待之外，其餘鋪都係倒模咁毫無新意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 場同場之間嘅接駁又係唔知做乜西，3期個行人天橋駁去新元中個停車場先再入去商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 預視到個場將來淨係會充斥住愈黎愈多大陸閪，根本就係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eac44f96f00718fe0d1cb3b2b202069b61dfcc9","tid":273713,"uid":62337,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T19:14:59.000Z","msg":"總括而言 屯元天都係垃圾"},{"pid":"8ad1a35e1b0f9303e8d88dc0654fbecbe28468dd","tid":273713,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T19:16:00.000Z","msg":"新元中裝修之前好過宜家好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有mid town 啲鋪頭根本就唔適合開喺元朗"},{"pid":"f13ea2fa2ad553b371603ca0cb08beb7670d0982","tid":273713,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T19:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總括而言 屯元天都係垃圾</blockquote><br />\n都係無撚出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19815a4863125a787a0f58e5a189ddfcbf39bf81","tid":273713,"uid":16590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T19:19:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新元中裝修之前好過宜家好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有mid town 啲鋪頭根本就唔適合開喺元朗</blockquote><br />\n以前個中庭好撚大又高，依家窄到仆街好有壓逼感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" 