002a2771ff1c4b99889eacd220e0e106630334","tid":273713,"uid":121315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:22:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本無野行 又係倒模連鎖店<br />\n<br />\n以前3樓有繽紛樂園 , 8百伴好行好多<br />\n<br />\n而家都係寄望個近近地有個一田同個戲院 其實都不值一提</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新元中有過8百伴咩 元朗8百伴以前好似開係大榮華隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  新元中係開過家樂福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最記得個濕9溜冰場 都唔知開左有冇一年"},{"pid":"a6da7d8739ef2dbdcfd64d40951db82297141136","tid":273713,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:22:17.000Z","msg":"其實點分佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又mid town 又新元朗中心"},{"pid":"b394f92ff7cc4d4f23f6f11fb96a9153867348bd","tid":273713,"uid":56900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:25:25.000Z","msg":"vcity好行好多 加埋屯中d舖實用性高好多"},{"pid":"55231545c00376e9da3073581c7616e55baba17d","tid":273713,"uid":121315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點分佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又mid town 又新元朗中心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我深信元朗大既人 元西站果邊點都係叫新元中 改唔到口"},{"pid":"d1d0244559fc76edd0b9764549b2c35841d85bf2","tid":273713,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"yoho堅垃圾 好多掘頭路 要行回頭<br />\nd鋪全部都係果d 賣點可能係比帶狗 但係只可以推車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f9c073e564e2f0de3beda435c70f90b3410e10","tid":273713,"uid":6677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點分佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又mid town 又新元朗中心</blockquote><br />\nYoho town, midtown同grand yoho係住宅項目(好似係)<br />\n商場叫yoho mall(好似係)<br />\n新元朗中心係YOHO Mall II舊名<br />\nMidtown個商場就YOHO Mall I(好似係)"},{"pid":"6488e332799ffd86a7a290de485a979af4a7937e","tid":273713,"uid":109050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:46:15.000Z","msg":"除左有個戲院之外好似仲衰過v city<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但人地屯門仲有屯門市廣場咁大個場"},{"pid":"b8adaf7d57ed0d257c3b03644dd061c3ccdb07b6","tid":273713,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實點分佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又mid town 又新元朗中心</blockquote><br />\nYoho town, midtown同grand yoho係住宅項目(好似係)<br />\n商場叫yoho mall(好似係)<br />\n新元朗中心係YOHO Mall II舊名<br />\nMidtown個商場就YOHO Mall I(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前我都仲分到<br />\nyoho town 一期 (元龍街)<br />\nyoho midtown (東頭村巴士站)<br />\n新元朗中心 (輕鐵站)<br />\n<br />\n而家變哂形點, 我分唔到"},{"pid":"db31633fd4ce2f3d780d9dcef54d3fd22c907d55","tid":273713,"uid":109050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點分佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又mid town 又新元朗中心</blockquote><br />\nYoho town, midtown同grand yoho係住宅項目(好似係)<br />\n商場叫yoho mall(好似係)<br />\n新元朗中心係YOHO Mall II舊名<br />\nMidtown個商場就YOHO Mall I(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前我都仲分到<br />\nyoho town 一期 (元龍街)<br />\nyoho midtown (東頭村巴士站)<br />\n新元朗中心 (輕鐵站)<br />\n<br />\n而家變哂形點, 我分唔到</blockquote><br />\n其實好簡單,yoho mall 分一期二期<br />\n二期即係以前新元中<br />\n而第一期又分兩邊,一面係依家開左果個yoho mall 1,另一面叫一期extension,即係未開果面"},{"pid":"1b8fecd6dbb7479f88c0ba5493b6b99cc05c1fcd","tid":273713,"uid":101987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總括而言 屯元天都係垃圾</blockquote><br />\n乜屯元天係香港一部分咩？"},{"pid":"57f3d89b13d45791568949f35d402f8f17e9f8ad","tid":273713,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:59:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左有個戲院之外好似仲衰過v city<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但人地屯門仲有屯門市廣場咁大個場</blockquote><br />\n2期好D,1期真係浪費空間"},{"pid":"cc3dbfd0e70a1a2a69c7b9a4d0b0a664592db8ff","tid":273713,"uid":16590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點分佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又mid town 又新元朗中心</blockquote><br />\nYoho town, midtown同grand yoho係住宅項目(好似係)<br />\n商場叫yoho mall(好似係)<br />\n新元朗中心係YOHO Mall II舊名<br />\nMidtown個商場就YOHO Mall I(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前我都仲分到<br />\nyoho town 一期 (元龍街)<br />\nyoho midtown (東頭村巴士站)<br />\n新元朗中心 (輕鐵站)<br />\n<br />\n而家變哂形點, 我分唔到</blockquote><br />\n啲名整到一舊舊，衰都衰過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4397b9d8ff86bb0ce7ee275e29c8e025cd99be4f","tid":273713,"uid":16590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:26:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新元中已經淪落到係比人經過，唔係比人行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 格局差到無倫<br />\nMidtown 人流少、地理位置其實唔多好，就算開埋戲院個邊，都一樣少人流<br />\n你係元朗市中心熱到死都唔想行去midtown行街<br />\n求其入元朗廣場算9數</blockquote><br />\n無論嘥幾多錢裝修都好，佢由古至今都係比人由西鐵行去雞地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9e1b7ad08e1dddc3282d5311232150cf775473","tid":273713,"uid":77755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:42:59.000Z","msg":"非常認同<br />\n我唔識分咩一二三期但係我都唔撚明點解同一個商場想行晒兩part要行一轉戶外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3b70b654e7e9556506a4b4a23f80b7085965df","tid":273713,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總括而言 屯元天都係垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagree<br />\n有名你叫大西北<br />\n個度住咩人配有咩商場<br />\n百貨應百客"},{"pid":"7d2914ef37f2ea315c55ff2329ac9c2a7e937fb5","tid":273713,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dis